Iconic R&B group Boys II Men will perform in South Africa in April 2020. JOHANNESBURG - Legendary American R&B group Boys II Men is set to tour South Africa in April 2020. READ: After slapping incident, pope kisses nun who vows not to bite The End of The Road hitmakers will perform in Pretoria on 9 April 2020 at the Sun Area followed by the Cape Town leg at the Grand Arena, GrandWest Casino on 13 April 2020. Tickets are available from Ticketpro and range between R290 to R1,750.